{"tid":475642,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"警方亦提醒市民，大部分針對現實世界的法例均適用於互聯網世界","createTime":"2017-11-21T09:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T10:15:12.000Z","uid":159064,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9e126ab65ca759271f6fa243502f8f0f711541","tid":475642,"uid":159064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"警方亦提醒市民，互聯網的世界不是無法可依，大部分針對現實世界的法例均適用於互聯網世界，因此切勿以身試法，而偷拍行為可能干犯以下罪行：<br />\n<br />\n遊蕩導致他人擔心--《刑事罪行條例》第200章160(3)條<br />\n有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦--《刑事罪行條例》第200章161條<br />\n公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為--《公安條例》第245章17B (2)條<br />\n作出令公眾憤慨的不雅行為--違反普通法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/135108?utm_content=buffer7f88a&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F135108%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer7f88a%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=I3169T1L%2FPFmetaPytazgY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=23275f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/135108?utm_content=buffer7f88a&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"ac32e4926a95562f6ba6aef4f375981fee622949","tid":475642,"uid":28624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"報驚撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cfa8e7007193b5fe6a8432619ae004b4324f4a","tid":475642,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"Support Good Hope<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n#Respect #Support"},{"pid":"d2e15ac00e06b34811e55860616105c5725b025d","tid":475642,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"#lihkg不代我"},{"pid":"c262f7334e103028877127efd3b4ec2c9d26c537","tid":475642,"uid":52068,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,